Package: correspondenceTables
Type: Package
Title: Functions for creating or updating correspondence tables between two statistical classifications
Version: 0.6.0
Author: Vasilis Chasiotis (Department of Statistics, Athens University of Economics and Business), Photis Stavropoulos (Quantos S.A. Statistics and Information Systems)
Maintainer: Matyas Meszaros <Matyas.MESZAROS@ec.europa.eu>
Description: The package contains two functions.
    One functions updates the correspondence table between two statistical classifications when one of the classifications gets updated to a new version.
    The other function creates a candidate correspondence table between two classifications when there are ''intermediate'' classifications and pivot correspondence tables leading from the first classification to the second one. 
